  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220675917887\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220675917887\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160406_189/isuhani_14599062196810WRQ4_JPEG/P4055310.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"436\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:480px; rheight:436px;\" id=\"20160406_189/isuhani_14599062196810WRQ4_JPEG/P4055310.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033614F483F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160406_189/isuhani_14599062196810WRQ4_JPEG/P4055310.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/sally_friends\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/sally_friends/original_15.png?type=p50_50\" alt=\"sally_friends-15\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">어제는 우리 원쌤 생일이었다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">원장님께서 출근 길에 이쁘고 맛있는 케잌을 사오셨다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://ssl.pstatic.net/static.se2/static/img/emoticon/3_48.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'static\\/img\\/emoticon\\/3_48.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"static/img/emoticon/3_48.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033614F483F')\" alt=\"\">&nbsp;생일 축하 합니다 생일 축하 합니다<br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">사랑하는 원쌤의 생일 축하 합니다&nbsp;<img src=\"https://ssl.pstatic.net/static.se2/static/img/emoticon/3_47.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'static\\/img\\/emoticon\\/3_47.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"static/img/emoticon/3_47.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033614F483F')\" alt=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">잠깐의 짧은 시간이었지만&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">누군가의 생일을 축하해주고</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">함께 한다는게 좋았다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">선생님 생일축하드려요~</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
